org.usfirst.frc2084.CMonster2014.subsystems

Class LedSubsystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.command.Subsystem
      • org.usfirst.frc2084.CMonster2014.subsystems.LedSubsystem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.NamedSendable, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Sendable

    public class LedSubsystem
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.command.Subsystem
    The subsystem that communicates with the Arduino to control the LED strip. It uses six DIO pins to form a six bit number. Each number codes for a different led pattern.
